// RAPID template for a migration decision
// Example: SAP ECC to S/4HANA migration approach

| Role       | Person                  | Responsibility                          |
|------------|-------------------------|----------------------------------------|
| Recommend  | Staff Engineer (you)    | Analyze options, recommend approach    |
| Agree      | Principal Engineer      | Sign off on technical soundness        |
| Perform    | Tech Lead, team         | Execute the migration                  |
| Input      | Product, Ops, Security  | Provide constraints and data           |
| Decide     | Director of Engineering | Make the final call                    |

// FAANG rule: If you Recommend and another person Decides,
// your job is to present options fairly, not to lobby.
// If you are the Decider, you own the outcome completely.
